                            "**Text must be in quotes** (single or double)",
                            "**Comments** start with **#** and explain your code",
                            "**Python is case-sensitive** (print ≠ Print)",
                            "**Programs execute** from top to bottom, one statement at a time"
                        ]
                    }
                }
            ]
        }
